headline: KLA Corporation Opens $138 Million R&D, Manufacturing Facility in Wales for Semiconductor Innovation
summary: KLA Corporation (NASDAQ:KLAC) is one of the high profit margin stocks to buy now. Towards the end of May, KLA Corporation officially opened a new $138 million R&D and manufacturing facility in Newport, Wales, UK.
